flowchart TD
    A((Start)) --> B[Select filters: Specialization, Year, Form]
    B --> C[Click 'Generate' button]
    C --> D[System retrieves data from Database]
    
    D --> E{Data complete?}
    
    E -- No --> F[Display error and suggested resolution]
    F -. Correct data .-> B
    
    E -- Yes --> G[Sort students alphabetically A-Z]
    G --> H[Display report on screen in tabular format]
    H --> I[Select export format: PDF, XLS, CSV]
    I --> J[Generate and download file]
    
    J --> K((End))